    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for anyone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches on the side panels and a small, shallow dent on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some minor staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating condition. It is a solid, honest vehicle for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
