    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a reliable source of parts? This vehicle has plenty of potential for the right hands! While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone who loves a restoration challenge. Grab this diamond in the rough at a great price!",
